About NEET/AIPMT Exam 2020: The NEET (Earlier AIPMT) is a qualifying entrance exam for students who wish to study any undergraduate medical course (MBBS), dental course (BDS), or postgraduate courses (MD / MS) in government or private medical colleges in India.  The National Eligibility cum Entrance Test or NEET is an entrance examination in India, for students who wish to study any graduate medical course, dental course or postgraduate course in government or private medical colleges.
